paragraphs:
[34]
Mr. Suhatski contends that the Board overlooked hundreds of documents and articles without explanation. These documents included information about:
 Human rights abuses and illegal practices of the Israeli military;
 The widespread use of torture;
 The 2006 invasion of Lebanon;
 The 2008 attack on Gaza and the ongoing siege there;
 The illegal attack on the Gaza flotilla in international waters; and
 The destruction of villages "amounting to ethnic cleansing".
